            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            数百人死里逃生，徒步逃离“乱葬岗”，以坦克轰鸣，不给活命机会          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      兵器志                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                兵器志              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">兵器志</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">gh_e736dd2ba97b</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">以全新的视角，领略不同的资讯</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">阅读前点击上方蓝色字体</span><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);visibility: visible;">“兵器志”</span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;">进行关注，建立深度阅读关系！</span><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-bottom: -12px;margin-left: 6px;outline: 0px;width: 27px;visibility: visible;"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 334.6 286.9" style="visibility: visible;"><polygon style="fill: rgb(245, 202, 70);visibility: visible;" points="334.6,286.9 185.3,286.9 185.3,0.4 334.6,150.4 "></polygon><polygon style="fill: none;stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width: 6;stroke-miterlimit: 10;visibility: visible;" points="147.6,283.9 3.3,283.9 3.3,7.4 147.6,150.4 "></polygon></svg></section><section style="padding-top: 20px;padding-right: 25px;padding-left: 11px;outline: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 253, 244);visibility: visible;text-align: left;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);visibility: visible;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></span><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">加沙战场画面曝光，以军坦克隆隆轰鸣，枪炮声震耳欲聋，数百人死里逃生，徒步逃离</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">“乱葬岗”，现场着实惨烈。</span></span></span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="327" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100004470" data-ratio="0.5902527075812274" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSgThAbECNhPibT7liaAiat38AKJMNWwnN2yJOOrpSLs5VO8j5AHXyTmlg5OhuIEsjq5ibpm5msTFSooA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">前言：目前，以色列军队对加沙地区展开了大规模地面攻势，基础设施被接连摧毁，哈马斯多处地下隧道也被封堵，甚至医院也成为了以军攻击的目标，宣称医院是哈马斯的“窝点”，所以才将炮筒对准医院，尽管国际社会强烈谴责并呼吁停火，巴以局势仍不见降温，加沙宛如“人间炼狱”。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">接下来，让我们一起看一下，加沙目前情况如何，人道主义危机是否得到了缓解？<p></p></span></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;visibility: visible;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";visibility: visible;'>01</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;visibility: visible;"><p draggable="true" style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";visibility: visible;'><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"> </span><span style="outline: 0px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);text-shadow: none;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">希法医院，沦为“死亡区域”</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 251.076px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><br></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">据媒体消息称，在加沙地区，以军坦克几乎畅行无阻，与重型车辆穿越大摇大摆穿梭在加沙城内，一旦发现“可疑”目标，当即开火毫不犹豫，加沙地带最大医院希法医院，及其周边人道主义设施，也难逃一劫。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">报道称，希法医院曾是加沙最大、最先进的转诊医院，如今已经沦为一个“死亡区域”，据世卫组织了解，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">希法医院门口，有一处“乱葬岗”，那里堆满尸体，而医院内部的情况更是叫人绝望。</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="298" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100004469" data-ratio="0.5379061371841155" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSgThAbECNhPibT7liaAiat38ArDRneAxJa4icrKwXzb7CTuTBLozzKJzMZr9TnKaqsoUpfzcBXNuPV8w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">伴随着一阵阵隆隆轰鸣，以军坦克和装甲推土机围攻希法医院，并扣押了</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">5000</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">多人作为人质，其中包括医生、护士、病人以及无所躲藏的难民，该</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">医院工作人员呼吁，希望国际组织能为这些人提供保护，他们已经失去了全部。</span></strong></span></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1700466421179" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1700466421179"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">据悉，目前医院停水停电，许多设备因为缺乏燃料无法开启，基本保障食物也没有了，在这个艰难的情况下，以军士兵还在不停的向医院开枪，不少医疗设备被毁，对此，以色列方面并未做出任何回应，只是坚称，那里存在哈马斯“指挥中心”，还十分自信的放出所谓的“证据”，并将地面行动扩展到加沙更多地区。<p></p></span></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>02</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;">  </span><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以军的“证据”，漏洞百出</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 268.611px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">为此，以军针对希法医院展开了突袭行动，然而并未找到哈马斯“地下指挥所”的实证，公布的“证据”更是漏洞百出，说服不了任何一个人。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">例如，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">以军表示自己找到了一个哈马斯地道入口，还拍下了视频物证</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">但视频画面中只是一个被挖掘破开的画面，似乎确实有一个隧道“入口”在那，但以军并没有进去确认，只是在“入口”旁晃了一圈，强调这就是他们找到的“证据”。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="410" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100004468" data-ratio="0.740072202166065" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSgThAbECNhPibT7liaAiat38AMERo6DszgbpuTkeYOuBZNkCbXq6Ghy6wwQkFHFaMgHxzaOfRNTxejQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">细心的网友很快发现，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">这个所谓的“入口”，像是一个化粪池设施</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">经过对比，似乎确实有类似的化粪池设计方案，比如一些存储设施、管道设计等等。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">于是，外界质疑，以军为了寻找哈马斯，掘地三尺结果挖出来化粪池，真是闹出了国际笑话。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">当前，以军找到的“证据”不止这一个。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">还有</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">以军在搜查希法医院的时候，声称找到了许多哈马斯遗留下的枪支弹药</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">并做出了展示，但这其中，也有猫腻。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">网友发现，哈马斯武器本就不多，不可能遗留下这么多武器，等着以军“捡漏”，这个逻辑本就不合理，另外，这些枪支武器，更像是木质模具<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">......</span><p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">还有，以军声称在核磁共振室中发现了哈马斯的武器装备，但稍微有点常识的都知道，核磁共振室中是不能放金属物品的，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">如果哈马斯真的打算在希法医院驻扎，是不可能为了放几支枪，就让昂贵的医疗设备停摆。</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="406" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100004467" data-ratio="0.7341772151898734" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSgThAbECNhPibT7liaAiat38APZSiaTVjIujQvu8YJJNKxcuAv891C4Ft5kNZ4oN7TmLM41CVt8J7kKQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">随着以军“证据”疑点被曝光，国际社会开始怀疑以色列在说谎，所以提出派出专业团队前往希法医院进行调查，以验证以军的“证据”是真是假，攻击希法医院的理由是否合法。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">尽管舆论压力巨大，以军也做出了暂时性撤出，但希法医院内部人员还是被逼着离开。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">有媒体曝光现场画面，有数百人从希法医院逃离，女人们领着行李包裹，男人肩扛幼子，试图去寻找下一个“庇护所”，但如今的加沙，几乎没有一片完整砖瓦，何以庇护这些可怜的难民。<p></p></span></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>03</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;">          </span><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">轰炸希法，用意深厚</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 286.146px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">那么</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，<span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">以军为何要顶着如此大的舆论压力，持续轰炸医院呢？</span></span></strong></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1700466414018" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1700466414018"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">分析指出，以军攻击甚至占领希法医院其背后有着非常深层次的战略意义。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">首先，该医院建在加沙中心地带，靠近哈马斯行政机关，一旦占领该处，就有可能动摇哈马斯布局，还会对当地民众形成强大的心理威慑。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">另外，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">针对希法医院的持续性攻击，显然是刻意为之。</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="369" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100004466" data-ratio="0.6672694394213382" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSgThAbECNhPibT7liaAiat38A3MibEoZbzyvNW1nHX34Hw4aT8bOfyXicesh54A3DTXyPtSGiadKKuiadsg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">从战术上来看，战争时期控制医疗服务具有非常高的战略意义，将其作为目标，此举防止了士兵接受治疗以重返战场，很大程度上来说，消除卫生资源会破坏对手内部稳定，致使其怠战，失去反抗信心。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">世卫组织表示，连续的轰炸对医生何尝不是一种折磨，当工作场所遭到轰炸、生命受到威胁，医生该如何保持中立，这对医生来说，是很残忍的选择。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">从目前情况来看，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">巴以双方围绕希法医院问题都需要提供一份强有力的“证据”。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><p></p></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">以方需要证明，希法医院下面确实是哈马斯的武装据点，这才能解释相关军事行动的合法性，而证据必须足够有说服力，而不是拿出上述那些没头没脑的东西，糊弄全世界。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">对巴方来说，就得澄清以军说法没有依据，实属荒谬，不少中东主流媒体也提出相同意见，就看谁能拿出更有力的“证据”，随着事态发展，关于希法医院下面到底有什么的谜底，终将掀开。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">但在这个过程中，加沙平民不该成为军事斗争的“炮灰”，他们的生命应该被尊重。<p></p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">结语：关于目前的巴以局势，大家还有什么了解的吗？欢迎在评论区留下您的看法和故事。</span></strong></span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1472425959" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 &